title: Fantasy Time Machine + Undrafted Gems, Jimmy Handsome - Fantasy Football Podcast for 8/30
description:
Who is this year’s Cooper Kupp?! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason jump into the fantasy time machine! Find out which players can step up in 2022 and surprise fantasy football managers. Is there a late round TE value out there like Dalton Schultz was last year? Plus, the latest NFL News and more! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for August 30th, 2022
